We are intefacing the GDC dataset (cancer) from NIH.

the GDC is composed by:
a) programs ('TCGA', 'MATCH', 'TARGET', 'CGCI', 'CMI', 'APOLLO',  ...)
b) primary sites (Adrenal gland, Bladder, Brain, Breast ...)
c) cases, subtypes, tumor class ane stages
d) expression table for each case (patient)

